Trudy!

797
01:11:57,541 --> 01:11:58,625
Trudy!

798
01:11:59,791 --> 01:12:01,666
Du svømmer den forkerte vej.

799
01:12:02,708 --> 01:12:04,541
Forkert vej. Denne vej.

800
